PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	900.000	950.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	LANZHOU, Apr. 15 (Staff Report) (Reporters: Wang Yunqi, Special Correspondent Wang Guangli) Yesterday morning, immediately following the shift handover at the Lanzhou Military Region Artillery Corps, 16 organization cadres picked up their back packs and headed to the companies in which they have been assigned to help-to-build.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	950.000	1000.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	Corps political commissar, Li Weiguo, emotionally stated, "Since the implementation of the system for linking responsibility for party building, assigned cadres of the "hands-off" type are few, while the sense of responsibility for help-to-build has strengthened.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1200.000	1237.500	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	In the past, organization cadres assigned to party building were known to "merely stroll through". Some cadres assigned to help-to-build just came to the camp to wander around and take a look.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1237.500	1275.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	There were some whose train of thought did not lead them to be helpful or take practical steps to help-to-build, but rather use their energy to write documents designed to garner them attention.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1275.000	1300.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	In this way, the concrete results of assigning cadres to help-to-build were not obvious.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1500.000	1550.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	The corps party committee analyzed the situation and concluded that the fundamental cause of the above-described phenomenon was that the responsibilities of cadres assigned to help-to-build were not clear: whether or not they helped, the result was the same, and it was all the same regardless of the quality of their help.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1550.000	1575.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	For this reason, the Help-to-build Accountability System was born.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1575.000	1587.500	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	They stipulated that organization cadres sent to assist in help-to-build must have clear task targets. Whoever helps in help-to-build is responsible, and if the task goal is not realized, the cadre will have to bear responsibility.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1587.500	1600.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	Cash rewards and punishments will link the results of help-to-build to the visiting cadre's promotion and rank. If the unit is not assessed as advanced, the corresponding visiting cadres for help-to-build cannot be assessed as advanced.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1800.000	1850.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	Marked results have be gained from assigning responsibility.	0	0	0		statement
PLA_CMN_20080418.0046.sgm	0	1850.000	1900.000	TEXT1	unknown	unkown	Chief of Reconnaissance Zhang Jianjun, and Cadre Chief Song Shaotao last year each took on a company's help-to-build duties. At year end, the two company's had entered into the ranks of the advanced, and the two men were also assessed as advanced individuals.	0	0	0		statement
